Comfortable Feeling: Upper with stretch fabric, give excellent flexible and comfortable. Various size available. Our shoes size may smaller than others, I suggest you choose a one large size.
Quick-dry & Convenience: Water shoes are fast drying speed and easy to clean, made of high quality smooth material with good breath ability, which helps your feet stay dry and comfy, easy to get on and off.
Safety: Water shoes for men women are made of anti-slip sole material, light and durable. Thickened sole and breathable insoles with shock absorption performance. Soft and Elastic Heel.
Easy to carry and keep: Our water socks are easily carry, you can put it in your bag and take it to everywhere, no matter you go to river, sea, lake and ocean to play.
Occasions: BOWENBO water barefoot shoes for men, women, big boys and big girls. Perfect for beach, swimming, surf, pool, sailing, boating, yoga, cycling, jogging, walking, fishing, car-washing, and driving with your family.
